Movement:

config.h - Stores all the key bindings that the player uses to move. 
handle_movement - Function in main.c  {Called in Main loop}
handle_mouse_input - Function in main.c {Called in Main loop}
on_right_click(); - Mouse right click
on_left_click(); - Mouse left click
set_block(); - Sets a block at a location to a specific block
client_position(); - Clients location within the world 
is_destructable(); - Checks if a block is breakable 
s->x, s->y, s->z - Player locations

